{
  "info": {
    "name": "ShowPass — Tutorial (até cap-06)",
    "description": "Coleção com todos os endpoints implementados até o cap-06 do tutorial ShowPass.\n\n## Como usar\n\n1. Importe este arquivo no Postman (File → Import).\n2. As variáveis `gateway_url`, `auth_url`, `event_url`, `booking_url` já estão configuradas em `Variables`.\n3. Rode primeiro **Auth → Login Organizer** ou **Auth → Login Buyer** — o token é salvo automaticamente em `organizer_token` / `buyer_token` via test script.\n4. Os endpoints autenticados usam `{{organizer_token}}` ou `{{buyer_token}}` no header `Authorization`.\n\n## Portas\n\n- Gateway: 3000 (entrada principal, proxy + JWT)\n- Auth-service: 3006\n- Event-service: 3003\n- Booking-service: 3004\n\nPor padrão os requests vão pelo **gateway** (`{{gateway_url}}`). Para debug, troque para a porta direta do serviço.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "gateway_url", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "auth_url", "value": "http://localhost:3006", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "event_url", "value": "http://localhost:3003", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "booking_url", "value": "http://localhost:3004", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "organizer_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "buyer_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "organizer_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "event_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "event_slug", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "venue_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "category_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "ticket_batch_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "seat_id", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "reservation_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /health/live (gateway)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/health/live", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["health", "live"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /health/ready (gateway)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/health/ready", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["health", "ready"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/organizers/register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (json.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('organizer_token', json.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Rock Produções\",\n  \"email\": \"organizer@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Senha@1234\",\n  \"organizationName\": \"Rock Produções Ltda\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/auth/organizers/register", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "organizers", "register"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/organizers/login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (json.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('organizer_token', json.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('Organizer token salvo');",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"organizer@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Senha@1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/auth/organizers/login", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "organizers", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /auth/organizers/me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{organizer_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/auth/organizers/me", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "organizers", "me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/organizers/refresh",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "description": "Requer cookie httpOnly `refresh_token` — definido automaticamente no login/register.",
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/auth/organizers/refresh", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "organizers", "refresh"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/refresh (genérico)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "description": "Rota genérica — usa o cookie `refresh_token` sem distinguir organizer/buyer.",
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "refresh"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{organizer_token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/auth/logout", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "logout"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/logout-all",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{organizer_token}}" }],
            "description": "Revoga TODOS os refresh tokens do usuário — útil em caso de suspeita de roubo.",
            "url": { "raw": "{{gateway_url}}/auth/logout-all", "host": ["{{gateway_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "logout-all"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/buyers/register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
